column1: Covid and Shutdowns - House Floor Remarks This Morning:  I rise this morning in defense of Governor Gavin Newsom who recently defied his own idiotic Covid edicts as he partied at one of the few restaurants that he has not yet forced out of business... https://t.co/2d6BBh31r6
1/3 I rise this morning in defense of Governor Gavin Newsom who recently defied his own idiotic Covid edicts as he partied at one of the few restaurants that he has not yet forced out of business.

I think COVID just made a big mistake taking on the President and First Lady!   Sending my best wishes and prayers to President @realDonaldTrump and @FLOTUS for a swift recovery. 🇺🇸 https://t.co/umf3CLzbSl
